    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Shutters having fixed slats that slope upwards from without, so as to exclude sun and rain, and admit air and some light. For similar shutters having movable slats, use "louvered shutters."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
